    <div class="straight">
      <div class="col good">
        <h4>What's good</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><span class="i">✓</span> Runs and drives — engine and trans strong</li>
          <li><span class="i">✓</span> Interior clean, no rips, AC blows cold</li>
          <li><span class="i">✓</span> Tires have good tread all around</li>
          <li><span class="i">✓</span> No frame damage — hit is cosmetic/front-clip</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="col bad">
        <h4>What it needs</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><span class="i">!</span> Front bumper, hood, and one headlight (front-end hit)</li>
          <li><span class="i">!</span> Airbag light on — front bags deployed</li>
          <li><span class="i">!</span> Salvage title — for rebuild or parts, not road-legal as-is</li>
          <li><span class="i">!</span> A good front-clip swap makes it a clean daily again</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

