      <p class="src">Reference: FTC <a href="https://www.ftc.gov/business-guidance/resources/dealers-guide-used-car-rule" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Used Car Rule (Buyers Guide)</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

